WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:04.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The Tony Awards
are this Sunday, and one of the
Broadway shows nominated for

00:04.866 --> 00:06.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
