look at what went into the
historical Middle East peace

00:12.833 --> 00:14.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
accords and their
relevance today.

00:14.700 --> 00:17.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
