story from New York.

00:17.000 --> 00:22.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: The world
saw this, the historic
1993 handshake between
Israeli Prime Minister

00:24.100 --> 00:29.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
