00:33.600 --> 00:37.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ACTOR: You will achieve nothing
because your negotiating
model is fundamentally flawed.

00:37.300 --> 00:42.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: The nine
months behind-the-scenes
secret negotiations
that led up to the Oslo

00:43.900 --> 00:45.400 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
accords.

00:45.400 --> 00:47.466 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ACTOR: This is our chance
to make a difference.

00:47.466 --> 00:52.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In the play
"Oslo," playwright J.T. Rogers
has taken real people and events

00:53.933 --> 00:56.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
