imagined his way into history.

00:56.900 --> 00:59.000 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
J.T.

00:59.000 --> 01:00.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
ROGERS, Playwright,
"Oslo": Sneaking into
the royal households in
Norway, the Palestine

01:00.966 --> 01:04.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Liberation Organization
illegally meeting with Israelis,
drinking together, talking

01:04.600 --> 01:09.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
