01:12.233 --> 01:15.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ACTRESS: A million Palestinians,
most of them without regular
electricity or water, crammed

01:15.200 --> 01:19.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
into an area 25 miles long,
but only a few miles wide.

01:19.233 --> 01:23.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Roger's way in
was through the little-known
behind-the-scenes role of

01:23.133 --> 01:28.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
