social scientist Terje
Rod-Larsen played by
Jefferson Mays, and diplomat

01:29.300 --> 01:31.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Mona Juul played
by Jennifer Ehle.

01:31.966 --> 01:36.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
