moment, for us, it began.

01:42.933 --> 01:47.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The real Mona
Juul is now Norway's ambassador
to the United Kingdom.

01:49.966 --> 01:52.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Her husband, the real
Terje Rod-Larsen, now
heads the International
Peace Institute and

01:54.400 --> 01:57.200 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
continues to work on various
crises around the world.

01:57.200 --> 02:02.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
