Israeli and the Norwegian side.

02:08.533 --> 02:12.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think most people had the
impression at the time that
this was something which was

02:12.200 --> 02:17.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
