it's your problems.

02:42.866 --> 02:44.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
You have to find
a solution to it.

02:44.666 --> 02:45.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's not our job.

02:45.866 --> 02:47.933 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It's your job.

02:47.933 --> 02:52.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: We watch the
face-off between Ahmed Qurei and
Uri Savir, the top Palestinian

02:54.100 --> 02:57.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
and Israeli negotiators,
played by Anthony Azizi
and Michael Aronov.

02:57.333 --> 03:02.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ACTOR: In my country, we see
you as terrorists and murderers
who wish to drive us into the

03:06.600 --> 03:08.733 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
sea.

03:08.733 --> 03:12.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ACTOR: In my country, we see
you as a savage nation whose
army shoots our children for

03:15.633 --> 03:17.733 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
sport!

03:17.733 --> 03:21.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Over time,
the two slowly get to know
and respect one another.

03:21.400 --> 03:24.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
ACTOR: Thank you.

03:24.533 --> 03:26.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I admire your passion.

03:26.766 --> 03:31.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The so-called
Oslo accords agreed to by
the real negotiators included

03:33.666 --> 03:37.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
